title: [Dev] Windows installer (MissionControlSetup.exe)
description: Build installer spec + implementation plan (NSIS/Electron Builder). Must bundle Node.js, install/config everything silently, create shortcuts, autostart services, post-install verification. No terminal for end user.

title: [Dev] Desktop app / launcher
description: Choose stack (Tauri/Electron/WebView2) and implement launcher: start background services, open Mission Control UI, tray controls, start/stop.

title: [Dev] Mission Control wiring
description: Implement Mission Control changes: user auth (email), tier selection, AI creation flow UI, usage widgets, budget lock screen, tasks UI for user AIs. Keep UI free of tokens/models.
